    • Constructor Detail

      • Truck

        public Truck(double posX,
             double posY,
             Direction dir)
        Sets the appearance, position and direction of the truck. Cars have an acceleration of 0.5m/s^2 and a random max. speed within the maxspeed range set by the simulation, at least 10km/h (i.e. 1.111px per tick).
        Parameters:
        posX - The X position of the truck on the scene
        posY - The Y position of the truck on the scene
        dir - The direction the truck should start moving in
